{"tid":895084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(美國) 今年已發生307宗大規模槍擊案","createTime":"2018-11-09T01:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T08:24:00.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"13044c6917a9118d187d7f738486bb797218fcdb","tid":895084,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T01:46:15.000Z","msg":"剛係加州酒吧又發生一單, 槍手為28歲白人男子伊恩（Ian David Long）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/how-many-mass-shootings-in-america-this-year-2018-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-many-mass-shootings-in-america-this-year-2018-2&d=Oghd3ciEbQH%2B5GyYlYTWVwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=6b9bc4ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.businessinsider.com/how-many-mass-shootings-in-america-this-year-2018-2</a><br />\n<br />\nThere have been 307 mass shootings in the US so far in 2018 &mdash; here's the full list<br />\nMelia Robinson, Skye Gould and Samantha Lee 7h<br />\n<br />\nThe number of mass shootings in the US this year has already reached 307.<br />\n<br />\nAt least 13 people, including the gunman, are dead after a shooting on Wednesday night at a bar in the Los Angeles suburb of Thousand Oaks.<br />\nThere have been nearly as many US mass shootings as days in 2018.<br />\nAt least 13 people, including the gunman, are dead after a shooting at a bar in Thousand Oaks, California, a Los Angeles suburb.<br />\n<br />\nThe bar, about 45 miles northwest of Los Angeles, was hosting a college night, attracting a young crowd.<br />\n<br />\nIt is the 307th mass shooting in 2018, according to the Gun Violence Archive, a nonprofit that tracks shootings in the US.<br />\n<br />\nTo put this into perspective, we are 312 days into the year, meaning the US has had nearly as many mass shootings as days in 2018.<br />\n<br />\nAmericans are more likely to die from gun violence than many leading causes of death combined, with some 11,000 people in the US killed in firearm assaults each year.<br />\n<br />\nThere is no broadly accepted definition of a mass shooting. The Gun Violence Archive defines a mass shooting as a single incident in which four or more people, not including the shooter, are &quot;shot and/or killed&quot; at &quot;the same general time and location.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThe government also doesn't have an official definition. In 2013, a report from the Congressional Research Service, known as Congress' think tank, described mass shootings as those in which shooters &quot;select victims somewhat indiscriminately&quot; and involve four or more deaths &mdash; a higher bar than the Gun Violence Archive's, as it doesn't take injuries into account.<br />\n<br />\nEarlier in 2013, a federal mandate identified the threshold as three or more deaths.<br />\n<br />\nAccording to data from the Gun Violence Archive, more than 12,000 people have died from gun-related violence in the US so far this year, and more than 24,000 others have been injured.<br />\n<br />\nHere's a complete list of the mass shootings, as defined by the Gun Violence Archive, that have occurred in the US so far in 2018:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gunviolencearchive.org/reports/mass-shooting\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gunviolencearchive.org%2Freports%2Fmass-shooting&d=Oghd3ciEbQH%2B5GyYlYTWVwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=bc4ebcaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.gunviolencearchive.org/reports/mass-shooting</a>"},{"pid":"9374be303298a926f2ae888b64be0aa7a7b0677a","tid":895084,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T01:48:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.worldjournal.com/5967788/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F5967788%2F&d=Oghd3ciEbQH%2B5GyYlYTWVwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=68506726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.worldjournal.com/5967788/</a><br />\n<br />\n【千橡鎮槍擊案】槍手Ian David Long背景大起底<br />\n記者張宏/洛杉磯報導 2018年11月08日 14:16<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/Qqeeqxg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQqeeqxg.png&h=62d10082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n千橡鎮槍擊慘案槍手Ian David Long導致12人身亡後開槍自殺，關於槍手的背景很多人都很好奇，是什麼原因導致他大開殺戒？<br />\n<br />\nLong住在范杜拉縣Newbury Park的一處民宅裡，他和母親一起住。根據CBS2報導，當地鄰居表示，Long曾經在海軍陸戰隊服役，曾是機槍手，2008年到2011年期間曾經在阿富汗待過。他在今年4月和警方曾經發生過衝突，情緒激動，此後心理醫師曾和其面談過，評估其精神狀況。<br />\n<br />\n槍手肆業與北嶺州大（Cal State Northridge），該學校8日發聲明表示對這次悲劇的受害者和家庭的慰問。北嶺州大校長Dianne Harrison表示，槍手是2013年至2016年期間曾在學校學習運動訓練課程，但是沒有畢業。北嶺州大對這起慘劇表示震驚，同時也對死者家屬和受害者表示哀悼，很多社區民眾都被這起慘劇所影響。任何人想尋求學校的幫助都可撥打電話 (818) 677-2366 。<br />\n<br />\n沛普丹大學（Pepperdine University)學生也有人在案發現場，學校8日表示，學校有幾名學生當晚在案發餐廳酒吧內，但目前還不確定是否有學生受傷或者死亡。學校在密切關注此事進展。學校8日沒有停課，不過學校允許學校如果受此事影響，可請假。學校將於8日中午在Smothers Theatre舉辦祈禱活動。<br />\n<br />\n千橡鎮也將在8日晚上6時舉辦守夜活動，千橡鎮市長Andrew <a href=\"http://Fox提供了www.VCCF.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FFox%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E4%BA%86www.VCCF.org&d=Oghd3ciEbQH%2B5GyYlYTWVwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=f953458e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Fox提供了www.VCCF.org</a>網站讓大家為受害者捐款。"},{"pid":"852aeb9cd574c67234e09d980a153aaef36c89c7","tid":895084,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T01:50:56.000Z","msg":"At least 13 people, including the gunman, are dead after a shooting on Wednesday night at a bar in the Los Angeles suburb of Thousand Oaks.<br />\n<br />\nr.i.p.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885a560f30da908120b52f264b169d74c0fb24f6","tid":895084,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T01:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e035725c9348c06d9c0a41497b662c140143404","tid":895084,"uid":147367,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T01:55:15.000Z","msg":"mass shoot